    <section xml:id="profileOperations">
        <title>Profiles</title>
        <para>Your Cloud Big Data profile is different from your cloud
            account. A profile is the configuration for the
            administration and login account for the cluster. Each
            user or account can have only one profile. Any updates or
            additions override the existing profile.</para>
